font-size: 12pt\\\\\">当晚，执法大队共检查了娱乐场所<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">40</span>多家。县文体新局副局长鲁俊新介绍说，除了经常进行这样的突击检查外，县文化执法部门还聘请了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>名退休老干部、人大代表等人员担任网吧等娱乐场所监督员，形成监管长效机制，有力保障了我县文化市场的健康发展。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-07/b166d469ea35b45ca47785ed65198f94.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n向娱乐场所业主强调注意事项</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1636','6','熊铁山、孙金龙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-08/6e0f33842e955bcd6a5920fe766cf9eb.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n在新街万亩精细蔬菜示范区调研<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>日，省国土资源厅党组书记、厅长孙亚到嘉鱼调研土地整治工作。市国土局局长皮凌，县领导熊征宇、余珂、朱从钦陪同调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">孙亚一行先后深入新街镇晒甲山村堤坡万亩精细蔬菜示范区、潘家湾镇解放渠基本农田整理项目区、潘家湾镇四邑村增减挂钩建新点、官桥镇官桥村增减挂钩建新点调研，详细询问项目区的规划、建设情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">孙亚肯定了嘉鱼在农村土地整治中所取得的成绩，</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">他指出，嘉鱼国土局在县委、县政府和市国土局的领导下，充分发挥国土部门的职能，做了一大批民心工程，在服务经济社会跨越发展、新农村建设等方面作出了突出成绩，起到了良好的示范作用。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">他希望嘉鱼县国土部门再鼓干劲，再添举措，切实打造土地整理利民、惠民项目，积极探索整村推进农村土地整治新渠道，打造企业、村民、社会多赢的整村推进模式。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，去年以来，我县建立完善了耕地保护共同责任机制，构建耕地保护由县到镇、到村、到组、到户的&ldquo;五级&rdquo;保护一张网。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年共组织实施土地整治项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>个，投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.5</span>亿余元，增加有效耕地面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9000</span>余亩。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">此外，我县还深入开展了国土资源节约集约示范县创建活动，以&ldquo;一张纸&rdquo;工程为基础，卡紧用地门槛&ldquo;一把尺&rdquo;，下好盘活存量&ldquo;一盘棋&rdquo;，全力推进矿山企业整合技改，合理调整和优化了全县国土资源利用结构，大大提高了国土资源利用效率，为我县经济建设提供了资源保障和社会支撑，被国土资源部表彰为首届&ldquo;全国土地、矿产兼有型节约集约模范示范县&rdquo;。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县国土资源局局长吴鹏陪同调研。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-08/aa2f107594f04599c4fd226ba29bcafd.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n在潘家湾四邑村调研<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1637','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-08/6b2a53eb5477664bcd6529f97c83f065.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">日，武汉至深圳高速公路嘉鱼至通城段初测初勘外业验收会在嘉鱼召开。省交通厅正厅级巡视员徐佑林、徐健，湖北交通职业技术学院党委书记熊友山，县委常委、副县长房健，副县长李德炳，及验收专家组成员、省市县相关单位代表等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">40</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">余人出席了验收会。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">与会专家和代表听取了勘察设计单位、双院制咨询和地勘监理单位的项目情况汇报，踏勘了现场，查阅了初测初勘成果资料，审查了初拟的设计方案，并就有关问题进行了充分的讨论。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">专家组认为，勘察设计单位采用的技术标准、路线的主要控制点和走向与工可保持一致，并结合沿线地形、地质等对工可路线方案进行了优化。初测初勘工作程序规范、方法正确，拟定的工程方案基本合理。专家组一致同意武深高速嘉鱼至通城段项目初测初勘外业通过验收，并建议在补充完善相关资料后转入初步设计工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">据介绍，武深高速嘉鱼至通城段起点位于嘉鱼新街镇三畈村，衔接武汉城市圈环线高速公路，并对接武嘉高速；经赤壁、崇阳，终点位于通城大坪乡达风村，衔接杭瑞高速，并对接通界（通城至湘鄂界）高速，全长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"> 91.4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">公里，项目估算总投资约</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">80</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">亿元，拟于今年</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">月开工，建设工期</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">42</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">个月。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">该项目是湖北省&ldquo;十二五&rdquo;交通发展规划&ldquo;七纵五横三环&rdquo;中的一纵。它的建设，将进一步完善湖北高速公路主骨架，拓宽武汉城市圈与长株潭城市群、珠三角都市圈的联系通道。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: right; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: right; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: right; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1638','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0608/20120608033724911.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">参观二乔公园</span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">至</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，新疆博州温泉县党委常委、组织部长张梦帆一行来我县参观考察。县委常委、常务副县长熊武华，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明陪同考察。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">考察团一行参观了二乔公园、环湖公园、嘉鱼县农村实用人才培训中心、潘家湾镇蔬菜基地、四邑村新村，元阳食品、中能锂电、联乐集团，以及官桥镇官桥村党员群众服务中心、居民社区，官桥村油茶、水产基地、官桥八组等地，对我县城市建设、新农村建设及工农业发展成果赞叹不已。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">今年以来，我县紧紧围绕加快建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城目标，紧抓发展第一要务，加快推进大工业、大旅游、大交通、大城建和新农村&ldquo;四大一新&rdquo;建设，抢抓机遇、真抓实干，促进了经济社会快速健康发展。元至五月，完成地方一般预算收入</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2.42</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，预计完成规模以上工业增加值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元、全社会固定资产投资额</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元、农民人均纯收入</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4714</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">元。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，温泉县是全国唯一以地热资源温泉命名的县，位于博州西部，南邻伊犁地区，北临哈萨克斯坦共和国，总面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5893</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里，平均海拔</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">米</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，总人口</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7.41</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万，居住着汉族、蒙古族、维吾尔族、哈萨克族、回族等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">19</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个民族，是&ldquo;中国北鲵的故乡&rdquo;、&ldquo;西迁守边察哈尔人的故乡&rdquo;。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0608/20120608033752917.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n座谈会现场</span></font></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1639','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0609/20120609025813617.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县领导认真听报告<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0609/20120609025905642.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体;\\\\\">报告会现场</span></span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>日，县委中心组举办&ldquo;历史的选择&rdquo;党史知识专题报告会，全国知名党史专家，湖北省委党史研究室编审、原副巡视员方城为县委中心组全体成员及各镇、各部门主要负责人和分管干部等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>余人讲授了一堂深刻的党史教育课。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;我们要坚定跟党走的路线，就要了解党的历史。&rdquo;方城教授结合自己对党史的研究体会，以丰富的史实、鲜明的观点、精辟的语言，围绕中国共产党诞生的背景、历经<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>个<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>年的发展历程以及今后党面临的新挑战和发展方向等三个方面，高度概括了党<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90</span>年艰苦卓绝的风雨历程，强调了中国共产党自主、自强、自律、自正、自我牺牲的精神，证明了中国共产党的诞生、中国共产党在中国的领导地位和核心作用的形成、中国人民走上社会主义道路、并通过改革开放和社会主义现代化建设实现中华民族的伟大复兴，这些都是历史的选择。</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 整个报告深入浅出，内容丰富，其中讲述的一个个革命先烈为了党、为了人民自我牺牲的历史故事，让在场学员无不感动敬佩。县长余珂说，听了报告深受教育，感觉再一次受到心灵的洗礼，深刻认识到尊重历史、尊重党史的重要性。他要求全县各级干部要深刻领会报告会精神，组织开展多种形式的党史教育活动，促进党员干部对党的基本理论、党的知识、党的历史、党的优良传统及宝贵经验的深入认识。要将学习活动与当前的重点项目建设、防汛抗灾、信访维稳、改善民生等重点工作结合起来，继续保持和巩固当前良好的发展势头，以实际行动和优异成绩迎接党的十八大胜利召开。</font></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1640','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0612/20120612105354501.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">县政协副主席雷家兴在卫生局进行提案督办<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0612/20120612105412821.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">县政协副主席刘平在交通局进行提案督办</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"12\\\\\" month=\\\\\"6\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，县政协副主席雷家兴、刘平分别带队，赴县卫生局、交通局等部门对相关提案进行督办。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在县卫生局，雷家兴认真听取了承办单位关于&ldquo;改善乡镇卫生院的医疗条件&rdquo;、&ldquo;偏远乡镇城镇居民医保和新农合亟待整合&rdquo;、&ldquo;依法打击&lsquo;医闹&rsquo;、保障医疗秩序&rdquo;、&ldquo;建立嘉鱼县医疗纠纷调解委员会&rdquo;等四个提案的办理进度及答复情况。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">雷家兴对县卫生局的提案办理情况表示肯定，认为其做到了领导重视、责任明确、措施得力，提案办理进度快、质量高。他要求该局进一步注重提案办理的规范性，承办责任人要掌握提案办理的方法、步骤和答复要求。同时，还要进一步在提案的落实力度上下功夫，在政策和财力允许的范围内，要尽量做到让群众满意。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在县交通局，刘平与相关提案的承办单位和会办单位负责人开展座谈，详细了解了关于&ldquo;营造企业宽松环境&rdquo;、&ldquo;加强城区公交车辆运营管理&rdquo;、&ldquo;加快绕县城外环交通线建设步伐&rdquo;等提案的办理进度和答复情况。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">刘平指出，各单位在提案的落实上要进一步具体和细化，要有针对性和可操作性，</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">承办单位之间要加强沟通配合，协商办理意见和措施，确保提案的落实率、见面率、满意率都能达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">。他强调，对于在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><a href=\\\\\"http://jyzx.cnjiayu.com.cn/tazz/\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">网上督办</span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">的提案</span></span></a></span>要高度重视，定人、定责、定时与<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><a href=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/bbs/forum.php?mod=forumdisplay&amp;fid=80\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">网民在线互动交流</span></span></a></span>，并定期汇总、公布提案办理进度。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1641','6','杨利','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0611/20120611080411652.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">为强力打造省级示范路，县规划执法局计划投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>万元，全力开展市容市貌综合整治。目标是做到垃圾清理不留死角，路面清洗要全面，广告清理要彻底，绿化修剪及造景要美化等。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"9\\\\\" month=\\\\\"6\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">，县规划执法局调动挖掘机、洒水车等车辆<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>台平整发展大道两侧建筑渣土；组织劳力<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>人对发展大道、迎宾路花坛绿化、行道树进行修剪和除杂；组织城管执法大队全体队员对发展大道全线进行综合整治，重点是对沿街广告进行清理规范，更换广告标语，对沿街占道经营行为进行清理取缔。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">结合治庸问责工作，该局对此次市容市貌整治活动规定了工作标准和完成时限，对未按规定的时间和要求完成工作的责任单位和个人将严肃处理。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0611/20120611080441279.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1642','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0611/20120611073933935.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">市县领导在解放渠高产农田土地整理项目视察<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>日，咸宁市政府副市长曾国平一行来嘉鱼县调研农村土地整理工作。市政府秘书长夏福卿，市国土局局长皮凌，县领导余珂、李国光、熊武华、朱从钦、李德炳陪同调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;以前这里是一片低洼地，名副其实的&lsquo;水袋子&rsquo;，老百姓的伤心田。现在这里渠道通畅，蔬菜产量高，而且道路修得这么平整宽阔，货车随时可以进出，种出来的东西自然好卖。&rdquo;在潘家湾镇解放渠高产农田土地整理项目现场，县国土部门负责人介绍说，为了改变潘家湾镇六贯堤、肖家洲等村地势低洼的现状，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2008</span>年国家开始投资实施了潘家湾镇高产农田整治项目，建设规模<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1982.9</span>公顷，成为湖北省首批建成的旱涝保收高标准基本农田。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">该项目通过平整土地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">101.7</span>公顷，修建沟渠<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">195.43</span>公里，新建田间道路<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">130.98</span>公里，将地势低洼、排水不畅的&ldquo;水袋子&rdquo;，建成&ldquo;田成方、林成行、渠相通、路相连、旱涝保收、高产稳产&rdquo;的基本农田。据潘家湾镇负责人介绍，项目实施后，不但改善了农业生产条件，增强了抵御自然灾害的能力，还有效提高了农业综合生产能力，促进了农民增收。目前，项目区农业产能提高了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20%</span>以上，生产成本降低了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20%</span>，项目区农民每年增收<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1800</span>万元，可以说是&ldquo;水袋子&rdquo;变成了&ldquo;钱袋子&rdquo;。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据统计，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2003</span>年以来，我县共投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8.95</span>亿元，实施国家和省级土地整治项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>个，整治农村土地约<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">33</span>万亩，新增耕地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.82</span>万亩，其中高产农田土地整理项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19</span>个，建设高产农田面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25.95</span>万亩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2010</span>年，我县还被列为湖北省整体推进农村土地整治示范县。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1643','6','施政','荆楚网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-13/7519441d71ffa4e56b274e89f93171d4.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;贯彻落实省第十次党代会精神，就是要紧盯建设&lsquo;湖北经济强县、长江临港新城&rsquo;目标不动摇。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，在湖北省第十次党代会第四场新闻发布会上，党代表、嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇说。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在熊征宇看来，嘉鱼建设&ldquo;湖北经济强县、长江临港新城&rdquo;，就是要实现&ldquo;三化&rdquo;协调，加快大园区和大项目、鱼米之乡、旅游胜地、临港新城的建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">建大园区和大项目。熊征宇介绍，嘉鱼将按照工业园区化、产业集群化的思路，重点围绕培育纺织、建材、管材、精细化工、食品加工和新能源等&ldquo;六大产业集群&rdquo;，尽快打造一批年产值过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元、过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元的产业集群。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">建设鱼米之乡。嘉鱼是全省的蔬菜大县、水产大县，特别是蔬菜产业享有&ldquo;北有寿光、南有嘉鱼&rdquo;之美誉。熊征宇说，嘉鱼将重点抓好潘家湾露天蔬菜标准园、渡普名优水产品等八大农业示范区建设，着力扶持洪发水产、国美食品等现有农副产品加工企业做大做强。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">建设旅游胜地。熊征宇介绍，嘉鱼将着力构建环三湖连江、密泉湖、官桥八组生态文化和环子湖、珍湖、大岩湖休闲度假&ldquo;两大旅游圈&rdquo;，唱响&ldquo;诗经嘉鱼、二乔故里&rdquo;旅游品牌，努力把嘉鱼建成全国优秀旅游目的地。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">建设长江临港新城。熊征宇说，嘉鱼紧临武汉、背靠长江，城乡发展基础较好，将抢抓沿江开发、小城镇建设、城乡统筹等系列机遇，早日把嘉鱼建成宜居宜业的长江临港新城。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇说，嘉鱼将积极贯彻落实党代会精神，实现&ldquo;三化&rdquo;协调发展，力争通过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年的努力，使嘉鱼</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县域经济综合实力迈入全省&ldquo;第一方阵&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1644','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-13/ce81d3d96d1cfcf61a2f61eb3d264d7b.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">检查东湖围堤<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>日，省公安厅副厅长刘红洲，省水利厅副厅长史芳斌等省防汛指挥部领导一行来嘉鱼检查防汛工作。副市长闫英姿，市公安局局长周勇，县领导余珂、李国光、魏萍陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">检查组一行来到东湖围堤茅花咀险段、余码头泵站进行了实地查看。据了解，东湖围堤等内湖民垸民堤由于基础条件较差，一直是全县的防汛工作重点。茅花咀段由于汛期风浪较大，更是重点险段。针对这一情况，入汛前，我县多次投入大量劳力、财力，对全县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>处民堤民垸和东、西湖围堤进行了重点整治，防洪能力得到一定提高。在余码头泵站，三台大型水泵正在进行抽水灌溉。据了解，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月中旬我县对大、中型泵站完成了高压测试，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月底余码头、马鞍山泵站已开机，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月底至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月初，余码头、马鞍山、三乐、丰收、后垸泵站相继开机排水。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">省检查组要求我县各级各部门要认清形势，切实做好防大汛抗大灾准备，杜绝麻痹大意思想，早安排早部署，切实落实领导责任制，从上到下，各负其责，牢牢把握防汛工作的主动权；要加强对重点工程、险工险段的检查，做好充足的防汛救灾物资准备，确保供应充足、调配及时，应急人员要保持通讯畅通，随时待命，确保各部门、各环节工作不出现漏洞。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">我县按照省、市防指&ldquo;防大汛、抗大旱&rdquo;的要求，立足抓早、抓紧、抓实地做好防汛备汛工作。自今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月份以来，县委、县政府主要领导带队先后对辖区水利设施和在建水利工程、水情测报点及堤段备料库开展了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>次汛前检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>处水雨观测站设施已完成维护与保养，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日各测报站投入正常测报。全县已储备草袋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.1</span>万条，编织袋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">48</span>万条，彩条布<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>万米，救生衣<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">270</span>件等防汛物资。下一步我县将立足&ldquo;五落实&rdquo;，即把防汛责任、汛前检查、汛期调度、应急预案落实到位，确保全县安全渡汛。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-13/0b87aa44a5da34ae3f5b466983841444.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">在余码头泵站检查<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1645','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-13/6a593d4272ddae2dfaded80bb56985e8.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在农贸市场检查指导<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;你们看，这就是老鼠留下的痕迹，一定要进行投药和清理，这是创建工作的重点。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>日，省爱卫办副主任李建、省爱卫技术专家岳木生一行在我县东岳路一家餐馆进行检查，对我县创建国家卫生县城工作进行指导。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"6\\\\\" day=\\\\\"12\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>日，检查组一行在县委副书记李国光，县委常委、县政法委书记朱从钦的陪同下，深入我县背街小巷、五小行业、集贸市场等地，就环境卫生、食品安全、虫霉防治、市容市貌等情况进行现场指导。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李建表示，我县对创建国家卫生县城工作高度重视，有决心，魄力大，取得了较大成效。他建议我县要进一步加强对创卫工作的领导，职能部门之间要密切配合，落实责任，狠抓重点，突破难点，特别是要加强对农贸市场活禽宰杀、小餐馆等五小行业的管理。要进一步制定垃圾处理厂方案，落实好责任。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">朱丛钦指出，创建国家卫生县城，是更好地促进全县经济社会持续快速健康发展的重大举措。各级各部门要认真领会落实专家组提出的宝贵意见建议，坚定创卫信心，一鼓作气，突出重点，攻克难点，科学规划，努力实现创建国家卫生县城的目标。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委宣传部常务副部长、县创建办常务副主任雷申会陪同了检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-13/2209cce679b62ab83cb7fc02914c0a91.jpg\\\\\" /></font></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在小餐馆检查指导</font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1646','6','熊铁山、石拥军','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-14/3f80281e5b149ceb76cac458ed185dc6.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">在武汉新概念公司检查</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>日，由市安监局副局长邢义鸣带队的市政府督查组来到嘉鱼，通过检查企业、查阅资料、听取汇报等形式，对我县&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;专项行动进行督查。副县长许隆高陪同督查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">许隆高对我县&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;专项行动进行了汇报。一季度以来，我县对全县范围内的违法违规生产经营行为进行了严厉打击。截至目前，共组织各类执法行动<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>次，出动执法人员<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">52</span>人次，检查企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">160</span>家，发现隐患<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">298</span>处。其中已整改<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">287</span>处，整改率<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">96%</span>；督促企业投入整改资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>万元，责令停产整顿<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>处，实施经济处罚<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>家。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">督查组表示，嘉鱼县委、县政府对&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;工作高度重视，安全生产责任落实到位，工作措施扎实有力；各部门&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;思路、方案正确，希望我县将良好的势头保持下去，确保全县安全生产形势持续稳定。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1-5</span>月，我县共发生各类生产安全事故<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>起（交通事故和消防火灾），同比下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.8%</span>；死亡<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>人，重伤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>人，同比下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12.5%</span>；直接经济损失<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25300</span>元，同比下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6.6%</span>；工矿商贸等实现了生产安全零事故，全县安全生产保持了总体平稳态势。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-14/20e3b8f15fef19ad6ded86d604d1a3f3.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1647','6','周艳、沈阳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-14/693d58ce5f7a8a69c82263d8a36db367.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n施工现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>日，县政协主席葛婷、副县长李德炳一行赴南门大道，对该项目的建设情况进行现场督办。县住建局局长尹彬生陪同督办。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">葛婷一行来到施工现场，实地查看了项目建设进展情况，并且就路基的碾压标准、碎石的铺垫厚度询问了施工负责人。据了解，目前南门大道已完成排水管铺设<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>米，正在进行主路基清理碾压工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">葛婷指出，高标准建设就是节约、低标准建设就是浪费，与其日后重复维修，不如一次性高标准建好。她要求施工单位在保证工程质量的前提下，抢抓晴好天气、加快施工进度、做好这一民生工程。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1648','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-14/78f76e01c152bab0ec4f1e2a51d18a8f.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">考察金亮织带生产车间<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">月</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">日，咸安区政协副主席邓仁栋带领考察团赴嘉鱼县，就我县乡镇工业园建设及发展情况开展考察调研。县政协副主席雷家兴陪同考察。</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">考察团一行先后实地考察了潘家湾镇畈湖工业园、鱼岳镇工业园，并深入部分企业的车间厂房，了解生产流程，听取企业负责人有关生产经营情况的介绍。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">在随后召开的座谈会上，雷家兴向考察团介绍了我县乡镇工业园的基本情况。他说，近年来，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">以县经济开发区为样本和参照，全县</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">各</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">镇工业园如雨后春笋般发展</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">潘家湾镇畈湖工业园已落户</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">68<font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家精细</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">化工企业，成功晋级为市级化工产业园；高铁岭镇做精</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">石头</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">文章，引进投资过亿元的葛洲坝水泥、高强锰业两家</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">龙头</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">企业</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，打造临江建材产业园</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">；陆溪镇则以方圆船舶制造为依托，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">打造船舶制造工业园。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">邓仁栋说，通过实地参观和听取介绍，深刻</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">感受到了嘉鱼县在镇域经济发展中的亮点。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">尤其是&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">的发展理念，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">因地制宜</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">打造特色镇，明确产业发展方向，实现一镇一产的集聚发展效应的规划举措，使考察团一行深受启发。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">他表示，将把这次在嘉鱼学习到的先进经验带回咸安，积极为咸安镇域经济的发展出谋划策、破解难题。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">与会的两地相关部门负责人就如何发展壮大镇级工业园这一主题，进行了深入的交流和讨论。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-14/3d596a4e80f6ca32fa35d7d89083393e.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">座谈会现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1653','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日上午，我县组织收听收看全省农作物重大病虫害防控工作电视电话会议，会议总结了上半年的病虫害防治工作，对治理当前作物重大病虫害防控工作做出安排部署。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会上，我省两个粮食主产区襄阳市、荆门市分别作典型发言，介绍了农作物重大病虫害防控工作情况。据省农业厅介绍，今年我省阴雨寡照，农作物病虫害面临多年来最为严重的防控形势。虫口夺粮是保证秋粮丰收，全年粮食实现<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>连增的重要保障。我省作为全国第十大粮食主产区，第五大水稻主产区，做好农作物重大病虫害防控工作不仅关系到农民增收，而且关系到国家粮食安全。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">副省长赵斌要求全省各地要统一思想，提高认识，增强做好农作物病虫害防治的紧迫感和责任感，迅速行动，多措并举，全面落实各项防控措施，加强统防统治，打响虫口夺粮的三夏战役，确保我省粮食丰收，为实现全省第十次党代会提出的奋斗目标努力奋斗。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1654','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-18/d9587438b735299f5c8a181d7ea76cfc.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在四邑新村了解项目建设情况<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>日，市长任振鹤来嘉鱼调研农村土地整治工作，市政府秘书长夏福卿，市国土局局长皮凌，县领导熊征宇、余珂、李国光、朱从钦、李德炳等陪同调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">任振鹤一行先后深入新街镇晒甲山村堤坡万亩精细蔬菜示范区、潘家湾镇解放渠基本农田土地整理项目、潘家湾镇四邑村增减挂钩建新点进行了实地查看，了解项目区的规划、建设情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">新街镇晒甲山村堤坡万亩精细蔬菜示范区于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2009</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月开始实施，建设规模<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1495.21</span>公顷，总投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3218.25</span>万元，新增耕地面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">45.03</span>公顷。该项目在建设稳产高产农田的同时，注重与市场做好对接，培植精细蔬菜基地，调整种植机构，使农民收入由土地整理前每年每亩<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.8</span>万元提高到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.5</span>万元以上。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">潘家湾镇解放渠高产农田土地整理项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2008</span>年由国家投资实施，建设规模<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1982.9</span>公顷，是湖北省首批建成的旱涝保收高标准基本农田。该项目通过平整土地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">101.7</span>公顷，修建沟渠<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">195.43</span>公里，新建田间道路<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">130.98</span>公里。目前，项目区农业产能提高了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20%</span>以上，生产成本降低了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20%</span>，农民每年增收<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1800</span>万元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">为了切实改善农民生产生活条件，使群众在土地整治中真正得实惠，潘家湾镇联手联乐集团，将农村土地整治与城乡建设用地增减挂钩相叠加，开展了潘家湾镇四邑村新农村建设。该项目将该镇四邑村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">170</span>户农户整体搬迁，建成占地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>亩可容纳<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">170</span>户村民入住、设施齐全、功能完备的新村，节约建设用地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">320</span>亩，目前新村主体工程已完工。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2003</span>年以来，我县共投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8.95</span>亿元，实施国家和省级土地整治项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>个，整治农村土地约<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">33</span>万亩，新增耕地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.82</span>万亩，其中高产农田土地整理项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19</span>个，建设高产农田面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25.95</span>万亩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2010</span>年，我县还被列为湖北省整体推进农村土地整治示范县。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1650','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0615/20120615054742254.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县召开传达贯彻省第十次党代会精神工作会议。县委书记熊征宇在会上作重要讲话，县委副书记、县长余珂主持会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇首先传达了省第十次党代会的精神，随后就学习贯彻会议精神，结合我县当前各项工作作了安排部署。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇指出，要认真学习、深刻领会省第十次党代会精神，迅速把思想和行动统一到省委的决策部署上来。要通过学习，不断深化对大会的主题、今后五年工作的指导思想、奋斗目标、工作举措的认识，切实把思想和行动高度统一到省委对全省经济、政治、文化、社会和党的建设战略部署上来。特别要深刻理解和把握李鸿忠书记在报告中提出的&ldquo;一个主题&rdquo;、&ldquo;两大目标&rdquo;和&ldquo;五个湖北&rdquo;的丰富内涵。全县上下要自觉按照党代会的精神来想问题、定规划、做决策、抓落实。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇要求，贯彻省第十次党代会精神，要强化机遇意识，以&ldquo;等不起&rdquo;的紧迫感、&ldquo;慢不得&rdquo;的危机感、&ldquo;坐不住&rdquo;的责任感，深入推进&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;建设，搭建承接产业转移的良好平台，紧盯大项目、大集团，力争引进一批中国</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">强甚至世界</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">强企业落户嘉鱼，增强发展后劲；要强化创新意识，坚持先行先试，大胆探索创新，建立健全招商引资、土地管理、企业融资、项目建设、人才选用等体制机制，促推全县经济社会发展逐步走上创新驱动的良性轨道；要强化进位意识，坚持工业第一战略，项目第一抓手，环境第一要素，努力在全县形成你追我赶、抢前争先的良好局面，奋力提升各项工作在全省的位次，赢得发展的主动权；要强化担当意识，面对不断凸现的新情况、新问题，全县各级领导干部必须敢闯敢干、敢作敢为、敢于担当。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇强调，全县上下要以学习贯彻省第十次党代会精神为动力，立足当前，抓好各项重点工作。各镇、各部门要进一步加大工作力度，确保上半年各项任务全面完成；要继续抓紧抓好重点项目建设，巩固&ldquo;百日大招商&rdquo;成果，争取项目早落地、早开工、早见效；要做好全国土地整治工作现场会的各项筹备工作，充分展示嘉鱼经济社会发展成果和良好对外形象；要切实<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">抓好防汛备汛、安全生产、计划生育等工作；要扎实做好信访维稳工作，为经济社会发展创造和谐稳定的环境。</span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂主持会议，他要求各单位党组织要迅速组织召开专题会议，向广大党员干部传达省第十次党代会精神；宣传部门要邀请专家为各级领导干部解读会议精神，县电视台、网站要开辟专栏，宣传会议精神；各单位要以会议精神为指导，强化举措，认真抓好工作落实。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">在家的县四大家领导、县委委员、县委候补委员、县人武部政委、县&ldquo;两办&rdquo;主任、县法院院长、县检察院检察长、县公安局局长、县纪委常委、县直各单位主要负责人、各镇党委书记、镇长出席会议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1651','6','周艳、沈阳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-16/bbb950e01e7fa398dc871399789a6602.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n施工现场<br />\r\n</font></font></span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日，县长余珂、县政协主席葛婷、副县长李德炳一行检查督办老城区道路改造项目。县住建局局长尹彬生陪同督办。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">余珂一行先后前往南门大道、岳公路、凤凰大道、通江路、龙潭大道、东岳路等项目现场，每到一处，他都详细询问工程进展情况，认真了解下一步施工措施，并对建设过程中出现的困难和问题做出了具体指示。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">余珂要求，住建部门要继续全力推进老城区道路改造工作，狠抓各项工作落实，协调解决项目建设中存在的问题和困难，确保项目早日建成。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">余珂强调，老城区道路改造是一项切实关系到民生的重要工程。要及时化解施工中出现的各类矛盾问题，在时间紧、任务重的情况下，要确保工程施工质量，加快工程建设速度，确保重点项目顺利推进。</font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1652','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-16/2f43d2654fb303dd15f343c1ba026d77.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">工人观看安全生产知识展板<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日，我县在电信广场开展了安全生产日咨询活动。副县长许隆高参加了活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">当天上午，县安监、消防、交警、质监、供电等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>个部门和单位工作人员来到电信广场，进行安全生产宣传，解答群众的咨询。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">许隆高向参加活动的各单位负责人强调，抓好安全生产不是一朝一夕的事，要时刻保持安全生产意识，加强对员工和群众的安全教育，在发展的同时讲安全，以安全保证发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">火灾逃生自救十法是什么？安全检查中有哪<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>五忌<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>？习惯性违章会有什么后果？这次宣传活动中，各单位结合本行业实际，把这些简单实用的安全知识用展板一一展示，并发放了相关宣传资料。县安监局还在现场进行了安全生产知识有奖竞赛活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月是全国第<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>个安全生产月，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>科学发展、安全发展<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>是今年安全生产月的主题。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月份我县还将开展安全知识下基层、发送安全生产公益短信、创建&ldquo;平安校园&rdquo;、消防演练等一系列丰富多彩的活动。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-16/76f2b7ce50413e9adc67372032fd0714.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县领导了解消防设施</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1655','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-18/d46e6a8b13143e571a2cb8ba4647c774.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">嘉鱼分会场现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"6\\\\\" day=\\\\\"15\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，全省质量兴省工作暨第三届长江质量奖颁奖电视电话会议召开。县长余珂、副县长许隆高出席嘉鱼分会场会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议指出，质量兴省战略实施以来，我省质量工作一步一个脚印，踏踏实实地向前推进，取得了可喜成绩，呈现出了工作推进的层次高、质量奖励的措施实、精品名牌产品培育的力度大、质量管理的要求严、质量技术支撑的平台宽等特点，不仅走在了全国的前列，而且创造出了很多的先进经验，在兄弟省市中引起了强烈的反响，受到了国家质检总局领导的好评。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议要求，全省上下直面湖北的实际，清醒认识到我省产品质量、工程质量、服务质量和环境质量与沿海先进地区、世界先进水平的较大差距，奋起直追。要不折不扣贯彻落实国务院及省政府质量发展《纲要》、要充分发挥企业主体作用、要大力推行卓越绩效管理、要坚持不懈地培育精品名牌产品、要严格质量安全监管、要继续建设完善质量技术检测平台。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议强调，质量兴省战略事关我省经济社会发展的全局，各级政府和有关部门都要积极行动起来，加强领导、加大投入、加强宣传、形成合力，共同推进质量兴省，以质量振兴促进湖北经济跨越式发展。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议还表彰了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度全省实施质量兴省战略工作先进单位，并对四家获得长江质量奖的企业各奖励人民币</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，对获得提名奖的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家企业各奖励人民币</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1656','6','刘蒙、李劲峰','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-19/8bd8d6d791e75e376e3484a38b1cde4e.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">参观咸宁市反腐倡廉成果图片展<br />\r\n<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-19/c4f9a0737baaf6d71d731ab3d645f763.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n听取服刑人员现身说法</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"19\\\\\" month=\\\\\"6\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19</span>日</st1:chsdate>，嘉鱼县纪委组织县财政、卫生、民政、人社、交通、住建等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>个部门的班子成员和重要岗位负责人共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">140</span>余人赴咸宁监狱接受警示教育。这次活动，既是全县第十三个党风廉政建设宣教月活动的重要内容之一，也是完善反腐倡廉预警防控机制的新探索。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">参加活动的人员一起参观了服刑人员的生产、生活情况，观看了咸宁市反腐倡廉建设成果展，听取了正在该监狱服刑的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>名囚犯的现场忏悔。两名服刑人员以自己的犯罪经过现身说法，深刻地剖析了犯罪动机、原因、心态及犯罪对自己和家庭、单位造成的伤害，让参加活动的干部从心灵深处受到了震撼。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">这是继<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月嘉鱼县委中心组成员、各镇党委书记和各部门&ldquo;一把手&rdquo;共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70</span>多人赴咸宁监狱接受警示教育后，我县又一次组织重点部门、重点岗位的主要负责人参观学习，是警示教育活动的延伸。县纪委负责人表示，通过领导干部&ldquo;零距离&rdquo;接受警示教育，是为了更好地预防职务犯罪，加强廉政风险防范，体现对干部的真正关心和爱护。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">面对服刑人员的自我剖析和悔恨心声，参观人员触动很大，确实感觉到了腐化堕落的&ldquo;成本很高，代价很大&rdquo;。大家更加强烈地感受到人身自由的重要，纷纷表示今后一定要牢记党性宗旨，筑牢拒腐防线，珍惜现在的幸福生活、珍惜现在的岗位、珍惜自己的前程，严格遵守党纪条规，不该去的地方坚决不去，不该拿的坚决不拿，正确看待和行使党和人民赋予的权力，慎用人民给予的权力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1657','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19</span>日，我县召开农产品质量安全暨病虫害防治工作会议，副县长魏萍出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">近年来，我县大力发展农业标准化生产，在种植业上制定了&ldquo;一套七种&rdquo;主要蔬菜无公害生产技术操作规程地方标准、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">127</span>种蔬菜、茶叶、水果等无公害生产技术操作规程，同时大力推广应用以生物农药、杀虫灯、性诱剂为主的病虫害绿色防控技术。在水产业上，我县大力推广&ldquo;一个主推品种、一项关键技术、一套操作规程&rdquo;和&ldquo;统一饲料标准、统一用药要求、统一产品质量&rdquo;的标准化水产养殖技术，在每个镇创建一个标准化健康养殖示范基地，推广面积达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>万亩，占水产养殖面积的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80%</span>以上。为加快农业品牌发展步伐，我县积极鼓励引导农产品生产企业、基地和农民专业合作社开展名优农产品创建工作。目前，全县认定无公害基地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>个，认定基地面积共计<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">351880</span>亩，共认证农业&ldquo;三品&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">180</span>个，绿色食品蔬菜及加工产品<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>个。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">魏萍对我县农产品质量安全及病虫害防治工作提出了三点意见。她要求相关部门首先要思想上重视，克服松懈、麻痹思想；其次要行动上认真做，建立健全各项防控体系，提高应急防控能力，在病虫害防治上不留死角；最后要加强组织领导，确保各项工作落实到位。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县农业局局长邓卫东介绍了我县农产品质量安全和病虫害防治工作，分析了当前农产品质量安全和农作物病虫害发生形势，提出了具体工作要求和技术方案。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会上，魏萍还与各乡镇及相关部门签订了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年农产品质量安全工作责任状。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1658','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-21/1eba24314b28f800f741dde1f5e3498d.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">会议现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"6\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，咸宁市农业经济形势分析会在嘉鱼召开，分析全市上半年农业经济运行情况，并对下一阶段农业生产形势进行研判。市农业局局长汪松林，副县长魏萍出席会议，全市各县市区农业部门主要负责人参加会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议指出，近年来，各级党委政府高度重视农业农村工作，相继出台了一系列强农惠农政策，切实保障种粮农民利益。我市大力推广农业科技应用，落实农业机械购置补贴，因地制宜调整农业生产结构，农业现代化水平得到明显提升，农业生产效益大大提高。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议要求，下一步，各县市区要继续抓好生产环节和示范亮点，切实抓好农业招商引资工作，引进和培育农业龙头企业，加快推进农业产业化。同时，要科学防治病虫害，加强乡镇农技推广体系建设，合理流转农村闲置土地，将秋播生产工作抓早抓好，力争保业绩、保产量、保目标。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，今年上半年，通过抢抓春耕备耕和农作物田间管理，我县夺取了夏粮夏油丰收增产。全县夏粮面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8.43</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万亩，总产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14970</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">吨，比去年增产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">17.52%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。其中，小麦面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6.96</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万亩，总产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11969</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万吨，比上年增产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">24.06%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">；油菜面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">9.67</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万亩，总产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">9678</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万吨，比上年增产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">21%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">下阶段，我县将紧紧围绕建设&ldquo;湖北现代农业示范区&rdquo;，实现&ldquo;四增三突破一提高&rdquo;的农业发展目标，切实抓好秋粮秋播生产和秋冬农业开发，开展好农业抗灾减灾和病虫害防治工作，强化农产品质量安全和农资执法监管，推进现代农业示范区建设和农业项目实施，确保我县各项农业工作措施落实和农业增效、农民增收。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1659','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div id=\\\\\"endtext\\\\\">\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-21/5c69b41d724ac795d6baaf13c26b01fe.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">座谈会现场</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"> </span></div>\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid:  16.3pt none; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">月</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">日，由省国土资源厅副巡视员王友章带队的省安委会&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;督查组赴我县，就&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;专项行动工作情况进行检查。副县长许隆高陪同检查。</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid:  16.3pt none; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">督查组一行首先来到陆溪镇蛇屋山金矿，听取了企业负责人关于&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;自查自纠的情况介绍，并深入生产一线察看安全生产情况。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid:  16.3pt none; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">在随后召开的座谈会上，许隆高向督查组汇报了我县安全生产领域&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;专项行动工作情况。他说，今年&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;专项行动开展以来，我县狠抓工作落实，做到了思想有认识，行动有方案，工作有专班，打击有力度，活动有内容，执法有结果，督办有效果，形势有好转。在这次行动中，对<font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家存在安全隐患的非煤矿山责令限期整改；对开发区内一家化工企业责令停产停业整顿；督促整改火灾隐患</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">140</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">余处，行政处罚</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家单位和个人。</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid:  16.3pt none; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，今年<font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1-5</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">月，我县共发生各类生产安全事故</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">起（交通事故和消防火灾），同比下降</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3.8%</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；死亡</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，致伤</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，同比下降</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12.5%</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；直接经济损失</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25300</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，同比下降</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6.6%</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；工矿商贸等实现了生产安全零事故，全县安全生产保持了总体平稳态势。</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid:  16.3pt none; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">通过实地查看和听取汇报，督查组对我县&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;专项行动开展情况及全县安全生产工作情况给予充分肯定，认为我县领导重视，组织得力，部门联动，成效显著。督查组要求我县继续深入开展各专项整治行动，将安全监管责任落实到基层，确保实效，建立&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;长效机制，确保全县安全生产形势进一步稳定。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-21/8d54ec85c20c17f7e685468c7a73b5b1.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><span id=\\\\\"1340197225356S\\\\\" style=\\\\\"display: none\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>在蛇屋山金矿检查<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1660','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-24/b277a8938263fe50be671f2db951ee6c.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日上午，全省城乡居民社会养老保险制度全覆盖工作电视电话会议在武昌召开。省委常委、副省长张岱梨出席会议并讲话。省政府副秘书长骆新华主持会议，省财政厅、省人社厅主要负责人进行大会发言，省新型农村和城镇居民社会养老保险试点工作领导小组成员单位参加会议。县长余珂在嘉鱼分会场参加会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议要求，从今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日起，在全省范围内启动城乡居民社会养老保险全覆盖工作，年底前完成。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据悉，截至目前，我省有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">65</span>个县（市、区）已分批纳入国家试点，全省参加城乡居民社会养老保险的人数达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1729</span>万人。今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日起，在所有未开展试点的县（市、区）全面启动城乡居民养老保险工作，社会养老保险将覆盖所有地区。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议强调，实现城乡居民社会养老保险制度的全覆盖，是贯彻落实省第十次党代会精神的重要举措，是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>实现人人享有基本养老保障<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>，建设幸福湖北的重要内容，体现出党和政府坚持以人为本、保障和改善民生的决心。各地要充分认识这项工作的重大意义，把思想认识统一到省委、省政府的部署要求上来。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议要求，各地要加强组织领导、形成工作合力，加强政策宣传、引导群众参保，夯实基层平台、提升经办能力，强化管理监督，保障基金安全，确保今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月底前，符合条件的城乡老年居民领到基础养老金；确保各地适龄城乡居民参保缴费率年底达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">85%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1661','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-24/9987671ec15626936216c30a80470c2c.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">参观县农村实用人才培训中心<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-24/5642b950f4fdeede5827d3a5a1518de6.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">参观潘家湾镇全域规划沙盘</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">21</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，新疆博州温泉县村党组织书记培训班（咸宁第二期）全体学员来嘉鱼参观。县委副书记李国光，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明陪同参观。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">考察团一行先后参观了嘉鱼县农村实用人才培训中心、潘家湾镇党员群众服务中心、潘家湾村党员群众服务中心、二乔公园、官桥八组等地，深入了解我县在基层党组织建设、新农村建设、统筹城乡发展等方面取得的成果。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">学员们纷纷表示，看到嘉鱼城镇面貌日新月异，基层党组织建设开展良好，感觉受益匪浅，回去后一定结合本地实际，把嘉鱼一些好的做法、好的经验、好的典型运用到自己工作中去。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">李国光对学员们的到来表示热烈欢迎，他说，通过多次的相互交流学习，嘉鱼县与温泉县结下了深厚情谊，并希望今后两地进一步加强联系与合作，在工作中相互学习和借鉴，实现共同发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，温泉县是全国唯一以地热资源温泉命名的县，位于博州西部，南邻伊犁地区，北临哈萨克斯坦共和国，总面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5893</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里，平均海拔</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"1300\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">米</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，总人口</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7.41</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万，居住着汉族、蒙古族、维吾尔族、哈萨克族、回族等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">19</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个民族，是&ldquo;中国北鲵的故乡&rdquo;、&ldquo;西迁守边察哈尔人的故乡&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-24/477497eb3634efd8859c7130ae7cc60c.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">参观潘家湾村群众服务中心</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1662','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-24/72cc5d1e9b287813da8dca08e41e7fe7.jpg\\\\\" />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在潘家湾镇农田土地整理项目现场视察</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"6\\\\\" day=\\\\\"22\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">22</span>日</st1:chsdate>，省委常委、市委书记黄楚平，副市长曾国平一行，在县四大家领导熊征宇、余珂、李国光、李鹏谋、葛婷、朱从钦等陪同下，深入到我县新街镇晒甲山村堤坡万亩精细蔬菜示范区、潘家湾镇解放渠基本农田土地整理项目现场、潘家湾镇四邑整体推进农村土地整治示范建设项目现场，实地考察指导土地整治工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">我县是全国第一批基本农田保护示范县，及湖北省<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">46</span>个粮食主产区和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>个整体推进农村土地整治示范县之一。近年来，我县抢抓国家土地整治战略发展机遇，按照&ldquo;政府主导、农村集体经济组织和农民为主体、国土搭台、部门参与、统筹规划、整合资金&rdquo;的工作思路，有序推进了全县高产农田整理、低丘岗地改造等农村土地整治项目，使之成为保发展、守红线、促转变、惠民生的重要平台，大力促进国土资源管理高效运行，形成了县域经济和国土事业发展齐头并进的&ldquo;双赢&rdquo;格局。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">近年来，我县科学规划、统筹安排，按照&ldquo;集中连片、整体推进&rdquo;的原则，在新街、潘家湾、渡普、牌洲湾等蔬菜、粮食主产镇，率先开展了万顷农田综合整治，实现了高标准基本农田田间硬化道路阡陌相通、排水沟渠纵横相连的无缝对接，促进了粮食产量大幅增长，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年，全县粮食总产量达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">120</span>万吨。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2003</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">年以来，全县共投入资金我<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8.95</span>亿元，实施国家和省级土地整治项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>个，整治农村土地约<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">37</span>万亩，新增耕地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.82</span>万亩，实现了建一个项目、兴一方产业、活一方经济、富一方百姓的目标。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">黄楚平充分肯定我县农村土地整治现场规模大、效果好，达到了令人眼前一亮、倍感震憾的效果。他说，嘉鱼土地整治工作为服务全县经济社会跨越发展、新农村建设等方面作出了突出成绩，起到了良好的示范作用。他要求我县再鼓干劲，再添举措，高标准建好农村土地整治项目，努力实现经济、社会、生态等多方效益的互促共赢。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县委办公室主任章斌陪同了检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1663','6','熊征宇','人民日报','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">嘉鱼县位于湖北省东南部，地属武汉城市圈，是全国</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">116</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个基本农田保护示范区、湖北省</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">46</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个粮食主产区和</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个整体推进农村土地整治示范县之一。大体呈现&ldquo;一山三水四分田、两分道路和庄园&rdquo;的地貌格局。近年来，面对日益稀缺的国土资源，我们因地制宜，积极探索由&ldquo;粗放式&rdquo;利用向&ldquo;精耕化&rdquo;开发的转变。今年</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">月，嘉鱼县被授予全国首届国土资源节约集约模范县。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">多极联动守红线。按照胡锦涛总书记&ldquo;二十字&rdquo;方针，我县初步构建了上下多极联动的国土资源工作新格局。实行县委常委分片负责制、项目用地陪审评估制、耕地保护协管员制，打造县、镇、村耕地保护&ldquo;三级&rdquo;保护屏障；充分发挥考评&ldquo;指挥棒&rdquo;作用，出台土地、矿产资源节约集约利用评价考核办法，将干部的政绩考核、任用与国土资源管理绩效挂钩；县人大、政协定期组织视察和调研，为节约集约利用资源进言献策。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">规划引领促集约。按照&ldquo;产业集群、投资集中、资源集约、产出高效&rdquo;要求，统筹协调城市规划、土地利用规划、矿产资源规划和产业规划，把有限的土地矿产资源要素向开发区、城镇功能区和骨干矿山、重点矿区集中，构建了&ldquo;两区两城、两圈两带&rdquo;空间发展格局。科学安排各类建设用地项目预留空间，合理设置勘查和开采规划区，以规划为龙头，以规划拓空间，以规划控扩张，以规划引集聚，全县工业聚集区由</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个合并至</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个，矿山企业由</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">32</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">家整合到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">17</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">家。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">科技推动提效能。县财政先后投入</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">多万元，支持国土部门建立覆盖全县的集数字化、网络化、智能化为一体的&ldquo;智慧国土&rdquo;工程，构建了以信息化为支撑的国土资源综合利用监管平台。鼓励支持企业不断运用现代科技和先进实用技术提升单位产出。蛇屋山金矿通过对喷淋、洗碳以及冶炼生产工艺进行技术改造，生产单位成品金所需要的矿石量明显减少。矿山生产综合回收率由原来的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&mdash;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">提高到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">78%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&mdash;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">82%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">，每年多回收黄金约</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"公斤\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"200\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">200</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">公斤</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">，年增加经济效益</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万元以上。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">创新驱动挖潜力。坚持从创新管理机制入手，提高土地综合利用率。一方面提高用地门槛，以土地集约倒逼产业结构升级。以单位面积投资额为杠杆，落户开发区的项目投资强度不得低于</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">200</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">/</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">亩，落户其他工业集中区的不得低于</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">160</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">/</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">亩，对达不到投资强度要求的项目统一进标准厂房。潘家湾畈湖化工园区实施项目准入制度后，园区每公顷工业产值达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">多万元。另一方面强化批后监管，通过置换、租赁、嫁接、流转等方式开展&ldquo;二次招商&rdquo;。仅经济开发区先后采取租、划、转、换等方式，清理盘活土地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">多亩，金桦实业、申邦化纤、怡和亚太等一大批投资上亿元的大项目落户均实现&ldquo;零&rdquo;新增用地。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">示范带动惠民生。近年来，我们抢抓政策机遇，将城乡建设用地增减挂钩、耕地质量建设和新农村建设有机结合，探索推行&ldquo;政府主导、农民主体、项目支撑、企业帮扶&rdquo;的新农村建设模式，先后在官桥村、四邑村、净堡村实施了迁村腾地、整村推进新农村试点建设，腾出零散居民点用地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1060</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">亩，净增耕地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余亩。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2003</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">年至今，全县投入资金</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8.95</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">亿元，实施国家和省级土地整治项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">26</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个，整治农村土地约</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">33</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万亩，新增耕地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3.82</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万亩，其中高产农田土地整理项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">19</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个，建设高标准农田</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25.95</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万亩，实现了建一个项目、兴一方产业、活一方经济、富一方农民的目标。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">有限资源、无限利用。在推进节约集约利用土地、加快经济社会转型发展的进程中，我们将全面落实节约优先战略，以资源的节约集约利用，进一步推动结构调整和布局优化，加快把嘉鱼建成湖北经济强县、长江临港新城。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1664','6','嘉鱼网综合','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">26</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，国土资源部、财政部在咸宁召开贯彻实施全国土地整治规划、加快建设高标准基本农田现场会。国土资源部部长、党组书记、国家土地总督察徐绍史，省委副书记、省长王国生出席并讲话。国土资源部副部长王世元主持会议。省委常委、咸宁市委书记黄楚平，副省长田承忠等出席会议。嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇在会上作了题为《做活土地整治文章，助推经济转型发展》的交流发言。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议召开前后，徐绍史等与会领导及</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余名会议代表实地考察了嘉鱼县潘家湾镇农业科技园高产农田土地整理项目、潘家湾镇四邑村整体推进农村土地整治示范建设项目，以及嘉鱼县国土资源局高产农田视频监控系统、土地利用&ldquo;一张图&rdquo;综合监管平台。省委常委、咸宁市委书记黄楚平、副省长田承忠、省政府副秘书长骆新华、省国土资源厅厅长孙亚，市领导任振鹤、夏亚灵、曾国平，县领导熊征宇、余珂等陪同考察。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-28/7732c09ed0057039becb5338a28353df.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">向徐绍史演示国土监控系统</span>（熊铁山摄）</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">嘉鱼作为湖北省整体推进农村土地整治示范县，目前已建设高产农田面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25.95</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万亩。徐绍史在听取相关介绍后说，土地是民生之本、发展之基。大力推进农村土地整治，建设和管护优质耕地，是发展方式转型的必然要求，一定要进一步增强忧患意识、责任意识和发展意识，不断提升统筹保障科学发展和保护土地资源的能力和水平。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在潘家湾镇农业科技园，徐绍史一路看，一路听，一路叮嘱：要以土地整治工程为平台，切实保障农民的知情权、参与权和受益权，做到整治前农民自愿，整治中农民参与，整治后农民满意，让土地整治成为真正的民生工程。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">得知嘉鱼县今年计划投入</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个亿整治土地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万亩时，徐绍史给予高度赞赏。他说，建设高标准基本农田、推进农村土地整治是一项涉及多部门、多领域的综合工程，需要社会各界的理解、支持和参与；要加快编制规划、计划及其实施方案，将建设目标落实到具体的工程、项目和地块，确保按时、按质、按量全面完成建设任务。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-06-28/bfc387d776d07a3272bd6bf539ae1ab1.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">徐绍史一行在嘉鱼县国土局视察监控中心（刘蒙摄）</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在嘉鱼县国土局，徐绍史视察了监控中心，看望了干部职工，希望广大干部职工履职尽责，坚守耕地保护红线，执行最严格的耕地保护制度；积极防范地质灾害，保障人民生命财产安全；加强党风廉政建设，树立良好形象。</span></font>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1665','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">6月29日，在喜迎中国共产党成立91周年之际，县委书记熊征宇来到洲湾镇，亲切走访慰问在社会主义建设中作出贡献的老党员和生活困难党员，并代表县委、县政府向他们送去党的关怀，送上节日的问候和美好祝福。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">花口村的王旺生老人今年84岁，已有54年党龄，曾担任多年村妇联主任。在老人家里，熊征宇关切地询问王旺生的生活情况，了解到她常年患病，家庭很困难，旧房子倒塌后新房迟迟没有做起来。熊征宇</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">叮嘱镇村负责同志</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">要给予老人更多的关心</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">帮助老人尽快建好房子，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">及时解决实际困难，让老</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">人</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">安享晚年。听说</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">王旺生</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">老人退休前在</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">村妇联主任的岗位上</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">兢兢业业、尽职尽责</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，而且是建百里长渠的老功臣，熊征宇动情地说，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">您在党的基层工作岗位上，为党和人民的事业作出了不平凡的贡献，党和政府永远不会忘记您。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">随后，熊征宇又来到王家巷村老党员张光前家里，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">与老人拉家常，关切询问老人的家庭情况、身体状况和生活来源。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">了解到张光前曾担任30余年村干部，退休后，他自己开了一家农资小卖部，服务周边群众，并且经常用自己的经验帮助村民解决一些种植方面的难题。熊征宇</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">说</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，您</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">几十年如一日坚守信念、无私奉献，始终保持了一名共产党员的先进性，这种精神值得我们学习、宣传和弘扬。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">临走时</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">他</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">还勉励张光前要</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">进一步发挥党员先锋模范作用，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">积极发挥余热，指导辅助年轻一代的村干部做好村里的各项工作，帮助更多的村民解决困难。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，&ldquo;七一&rdquo;前夕，余珂、李国光、李鹏谋、葛婷等县四大家领导也分赴各镇慰问了困难老党员、任职满20年的离任村主职干部等共152人，并赠送了慰问金。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1666','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/c3b64200aee0ca0d7f308a8bc96d99bc.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">检查州丰收泵站运转情况<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/31d46ac30f1e8cee0d2b37de487497e0.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在陈家坊村检查灾情<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日傍晚，县长余珂、县委副书记李国光、副县长魏萍带领水利、民政等部门负责人到洲湾镇，实地察看灾情，指导抗灾救灾工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在洲湾镇负责人的陪同下，余珂一行来到刘家堤、陈家坊、金家洲等村的田间地头查看灾情。看见农田变成了池塘，蔬菜、稻谷损毁严重，余珂再三叮嘱镇、村干部一定要深入到农户家中，认真做好灾情统计工作，并组织好村民开展生产自救。随后，余珂来到该镇的丰收泵站，叮嘱值班员要明确职责，加强巡查，确保泵站正常排水。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余珂指出，各镇要充分认识到防汛救灾工作的重要性和艰巨性，提高防灾减灾能力，全面落实好各项责任和工作任务，并做好新一轮强降雨防范工作，全力确保人民群众生命财产安全。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">要在防汛救灾的同时，抓紧展开生产自救，抓紧组织恢复重建，抓紧补种农作物，努力把灾害损失降到最低限度。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">就下一阶段的防汛救灾工作，余珂要求，各镇要抓紧抢修水毁工程，加强水库、地质灾害点的巡查工作，排除安全隐患，全力以赴做好各项防汛措施，减少灾害损失。要及时统计、核实、上报灾情，抓紧争取上级相关部门的灾后补助资金，并迅速组织工作人员、技术人员分赴灾区指导，组织农民开展灾后生产自救工作。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1667','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/66cf74d4deef1eb45549f47f7c2132e5.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">会议现场<span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日下午，全县防汛救灾工作紧急会议召开。县长余珂、县委副书记李国光、副县长魏萍参加会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">余珂强调，各部门要高度重视，紧急行动，采取有效措施，切实做好防汛救灾工作，要紧急启动各项防汛准备工作，确保一旦发生汛情、险情，能够靠前指挥，有效应对；要统筹安排，科学调度，加快排涝；要迅速行动，抗灾救灾，切实做好被淹农田恢复生产的管理工作，把灾害损失降低到最低程度。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">余珂要求，气象部门要及时准确监测、及时发布信息、要分析入梅后天气和雨情情况，一旦有准确汛情信息<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>要第一时间进行汇报；电力部门要全力支持，做好电力设备检查和维护，确保各个泵站正常运转；民政部门要搞好核灾救灾工作；保险机构要及时做好灾后理赔工作，使受灾群众尽快恢复生产；农业、农机部门要深入灾区，为农民提供技术服务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">李国光要求各部门高度重视，从现在开始，全力以赴，做好防汛救灾工作。防汛指挥部、防汛办要<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时保持与气象部门、各乡镇的联系<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>做好信息沟通。相关单位</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">要严格执行防汛值带班制度，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">必须坚持<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时值守，保持<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时手机开机，保证信息畅通，指挥高效。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">魏萍主持会议并对下一步防汛救灾工作做了部署。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县气象局分析了入梅后天气和雨情情况；县水利局介绍了前段时间的水利工作并对下一阶段的工作作了部署；各乡镇汇报了前期防汛工作情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><br />\r\n</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/51339c9c982ce4720e3aab425b6ca823.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议现场</font><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1668','6','雷涛','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/2cccd43b587266b553d1a3c8d30dce88.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">推进会现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日上午，嘉鱼县召开清收农信社不良贷款推进会，县委常委、常务副县长熊武华出席会议。县纪委、公安、检察院、法院及各镇主要负责人参加会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊武华要求，各部门、各镇要切实转变观念，走出思想误区，正确认识到清收农信社不良贷款的政治意义和现实意义，加强横向联系，密切协作，强力推进不良贷款清收工作。县纪检监察部门要继续逐个单位排查，对拒不还款的国家公职人员，采取&ldquo;两停一限&rdquo;（即停薪、停岗、限期归还借款）的方式进行催收；县公安部门要大力开展&ldquo;清网行动&rdquo;，发挥经侦部门职能优势，深入摸排贷款诈骗、高利转贷、骗取贷款等破坏金融秩序类违法犯罪线索，发现一起，立案一起，查处一起；县法院要大胆适用简易程序，采取集中送达、巡回审理的方式，对清收案件开设&ldquo;绿色通道&rdquo;，实行&ldquo;快立、快审、快结、快执&rdquo;制度；各镇要根据自己辖区不良贷款的特点，有针对性的运用清收手段，在当地形成浓厚的清收氛围；农信社要做好协调、服务工作，确保完成不良贷款清收任务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县信用联社理事长<st1:personname w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" productid=\\\\\"万\\\\\">万</st1:personname>君明通报了县人民政府驻农信社清收不良贷款领导小组<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年清收工作进展情况，县政府办副主任古红武宣读了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年调整后的领导小组成员名单，各镇负责人就如何进一步推动清收进程作了表态发言。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1669','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日，县委副书记李国光、副县长魏萍率水利、民政等部门负责人，深入到洲湾镇和潘家湾镇，实地察看灾情，指导抗灾工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">李国光一行实地查看了洲湾镇刘家堤、耿家湖和陈家坊村和潘家湾镇复兴洲村的受灾情况。每到一地，他都详细询问群众的受灾情况并要求随行的部门负责人</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">迅速行动，采取有效措施，扎实做好防汛救灾各项工作。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，自<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>号入梅以来，洲湾镇和潘家湾镇连续遭遇暴雨袭击，截止<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>点，累计降雨量达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">223.5</span>毫米，两个镇都有不少农作物受渍。目前，两个镇正在开启全部排涝泵站抢排渍水。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李国光要求洲湾镇和潘家湾镇要把防汛抗灾工作作为当前的头等大事来抓，牢固树立防大汛、抗大灾、保安全的思想。领导干部要靠前指挥，科学调度，所有的泵站开足马力，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时全力以赴做好抢排渍水工作，力争将灾害造成的损失降到最低。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1670','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/9395176bfd26aa7faf99bffbb760cd80.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n为先进基层党组织颁奖</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/e1e8a43d8caf9e71e274261b3319f44b.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县召开创先争优暨全国国土现场会筹备工作总结表彰大会，隆重庆祝建党</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">91</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">周年，总结表彰</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2010</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度创先争优活动以及在全国国土现场会筹备工作中涌现出来的先进集体和先进个人。熊征宇、余珂、李国光、李鹏谋、葛婷等县四大家领导出席会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇作了题为《弘扬&ldquo;铁军精神&rdquo;、努力创先争优，不断开创嘉鱼经济社会科学发展跨越发展新局面》的讲话。他说，近年来，县委坚持党建第一抓手，不断加强和改进新形势下党的领导。特别是</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2010</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月以来，县委围绕加快基层党组织&ldquo;五个基本&rdquo;、&ldquo;七个体系&rdquo;建设目标，在全县各级党组织和党员中先后开展了创先争优、&ldquo;喜迎十八大、争创新业绩&rdquo;、治庸问责、基层组织建设年等主题实践活动，激发了全县各级党组织和广大党员干事创业的热情，涌现出一批先进基层党组织和优秀共产党员。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇指出，两年多来，全县创先争优活动在促进干部思想大解放、基层基础大夯实、干部作风大转变、发展环境大优化、县域发展大提速等方面取得了明显成效。当前，党情、世情、国情时刻都在发生深刻变化，对党的建设提出了新的要求，在下一阶段的工作中，全县各级各部门要总结成绩，坚定推进嘉鱼科学发展、跨越发展的信心；要把握重点，扎实有效地推动党建工作取得新成效；要提振精神，奋力推进全县经济社会科学发展跨越发展。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇强调，全县各级党组织务必采取更加有效的措施，突出&ldquo;四项重点&rdquo;，实现&ldquo;四个新成效&rdquo;。即：以强化理论武装为重点，推动思想理论建设取得新成效；以深入开展&ldquo;迎创&rdquo;活动为重点，推动基层组织建设取得新成效；以提高引领科学发展能力为重点，推动干部队伍建设取得新成效；以打造清廉高效发展环境为重点，推动党风廉政建设取得新成效。全县各级党组织和广大党员干部要严格落实党要管党，善抓发展机遇，勇于抢前争先，坚持发展为民，务求狠抓落实。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">对于本次全国国土现场会筹备工作，熊征宇表示，在全县上下共同努力下，全国国土现场会参观组织工作取得圆满成功，充分展示了嘉鱼发展成果和干部群众的精神风貌，得到各级领导及与会代表的一致肯定。全县各级党组织和广大党员干部以实际行动展现了全县上下万众一心、众志成城的协作精神，克难攻坚、顽强拼搏的进取精神，勇争一流、追求卓越的创新精神，不怕吃苦、任劳任怨的奉献精神，践行了创先争优。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂主持会议。他要求全县各级党组织和全体党员干部要认真学习，深刻领会，进一步发扬协作精神、进取精神、奉献精神和铁军精神，提高认识，凝聚发展合力；转变作风，狠抓工作落实；锐意创新，推动跨越发展。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记李国光宣读了《中共嘉鱼县委关于表彰</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2010</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年全县创先争优先进基层党组织、优秀共产党员和优秀党务工作者的决定》。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委常委、常务副县长熊武华宣读了《中共嘉鱼县委、嘉鱼县人民政府关于表彰全国高标准基本农田建设现场会先进集体和先进个人的决定》。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议为获得表彰的先进集体和先进个人进行了颁奖。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县&ldquo;两办&rdquo;主任、人武部政委、法检两长、公安局长；曾担任过正县职以上的老干部；曾担任过副县级以上领导职务的离退休老干部代表；特邀田野集团董事长、联乐集团总裁；各镇党委书记、镇长，分管组织的副书记，组织委员；县直各单位主要负责人、党组织书记；受表彰的先进基层党组织、优秀共产党员代表和全国高标准基本农田建设现场会先进集体、先进个人代表，共计</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">280</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余人参加会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1671','8','县住建局','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">一、建设项目的名称及概要<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">项目名称：嘉鱼县生活垃圾卫生填埋场工程<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">项目概况：本工程占地面积为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">129.8</span>亩，总库容量<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">105</span>万<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">m3</span>，日平均处理能力为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">150t</span>，使用年限为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16.9</span>年，服务范围为嘉鱼县城区及周边乡镇。工程建设主要内容包括：垃圾填埋主体工程，雨污分流工程，渗滤液收集及处理工程，生产、生活设施工程，道路工程，输配电工程等内容。项目计划总投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6957.39</span>万元。本项目采用卫生填埋法作为生活垃圾的主要处理方法，垃圾填埋采取分区、分单元填埋工艺。填埋场防渗采用<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">HDPE</span>＋膨润土复合防渗衬垫水平防渗工艺。填埋场填埋气体采用&ldquo;收集&mdash;焚烧处理&rdquo;的方式进行。填埋场渗滤液采取&ldquo;污水处理站处理&mdash;达标排放&rdquo;的方式进行。项目建成后将有助于改善嘉鱼县生活垃圾处理现状，美化嘉鱼县城市环境，改善人民生产生活需要，改善投资和旅游环境的需要，有利于嘉鱼县的可持续发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">二、环境质量现状评价<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">地表水：现状监测结果表明，自然渠及西凉湖各监测断面监测指标值均满足地表水环境质量标准（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GB3838-2002</span>）Ⅲ类标准的要求；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">地下水：地下水现状评价结果表明，各项水质指标均达到（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GB/T14848-93</span>）地下水环境质量标准Ⅲ类标准限值要求，评价区域地下水的水质状况良好；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">环境空气：拟建项目场址周围地区环境空气的各评价因子现状监测结果表明，各因子均可达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GB3095-1996</span>《环境空气质量标准》二级标准限值要求；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">声环境：拟建项目所在区域声环境质量良好，各监测点的噪声值均满足<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GB3096-2008</span>《声环境质量标准》<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>类标准要求。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">三、环境影响预测评价<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">1 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">水环境<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">嘉鱼生活垃圾卫生填埋场污水包括垃圾渗滤液、管理区生活污水及洗车废水等，填埋场污水经过收集后输送至场区渗滤液处理站处理后达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GB16889-2008</span>《生活垃圾填埋场污染控制标准》要求后，通过自然渠排入西凉湖，污水经达标处理后水环境造成影响较小。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">嘉鱼县生活垃圾卫生填埋场采用<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">HDPE</span>＋膨润土复合防渗衬垫水平防渗工艺做防渗衬层处理后，垃圾填埋场的渗滤液向地下渗透将得到很好的控制，可保证垃圾填埋场在多年正常运行的情况下，渗滤液对地下水的影响程度控制在有限的范围内。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">环境空气<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">正常工况下：敏感点和网格点处得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">NH3</span>的小时贡献浓度最大值出现在网格点<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">(200</span>，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">-700)</span>，贡献浓度占标率为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70.80%</span>。由此可知，项目运营期间<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">NH3</span>贡献浓度对其他敏感点影响较小。评价范围内<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">SO2</span>的日均贡献浓度最大值出现在石埠塘何家，贡献浓度占标率为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.15%</span>，出现时间为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日。由此可知，项目运营期间<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">SO2</span>贡献浓度对其他敏感点影响较小。评价范围内<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">SO2</span>的年均贡献浓度最大值出现在网格点石埠塘何家，贡献浓度占标率为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.29%</span>。由此可知，项目运营期间<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">SO2</span>贡献浓度对其他敏感点影响较小。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">非正常工况条件下，填埋区<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">NH3</span>、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">H2S</span>的小时贡献浓度最大值分别为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.409357mg/m3</span>、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.020723 mg/m3</span>，对应的占标率分别为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">204.68%</span>、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">207.23%</span>，所有环境敏感点和网格点均出现超标现象。由此可见，非正常工况条件下周边敏感点受填埋区恶臭的影响较大。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">通过计算得出：本工程防护距离为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500m</span>，在本项目环境防护距离内有部分居民需要搬迁，目前，嘉鱼县政府已经出具相关承诺，确保项目顺利实施。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">3 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">声环境<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">运营期固定噪声源对各厂界的贡献值均没有超过《工业企业厂界环境噪声排放标准》<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">(GB12348-2008)</span>中的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>类标准限值要求，对各敏感点的贡献值均没有超过《声环境质量标准》<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>类标准限值要求，叠加背景值后的预测源强也满足《工业企业厂界环境噪声排放标准》<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">(GB12348-2008)</span>中的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>类标准限制要求和《声环境质量标准》<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>类标准限值要求，本项目建成后，厂界噪声和敏感点噪声可以实现达标排放。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">四、预防或减轻不良影响的对策和措施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">1 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">水污染防治措施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">拟建项目渗滤液、填埋场生活污水及生产废水经收集后进入调节池，而后输送至渗滤液处理站进行处理。处理工艺采用&ldquo;预处理＋外置式<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">MBR</span>＋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">NF</span>＋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">RO</span>&rdquo;工艺，经处理后的各项指标均达到《生活垃圾填埋场污染控制标准》（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GB16889-2008</span>）的要求，满足受纳水体西凉湖河环境要求，可达标排放，污水治理措施可行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">大气污染防治措施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">对于废气的污染防治，通过采取气体收集系统和填埋气处理系统后，填埋场的废气被有效收集并焚烧处理后排放；同时辅以经常打扫、冲洗路面，建植防护林，及时覆盖当日垃圾等措施后，对周围空气环境不会产生明显的不利影响。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">3 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">噪声污染防治措施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">合理安排运输车辆时间和路线计划，控制好行驶车辆的车速；避开夜间施工，选择低噪声施工机械可减缓噪声的影响。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">4 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">生态保护措施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在垃圾场周围种植绿化带，以避免垃圾中纸屑扬尘对周围土壤和环境的影响。封场处理是在垃圾填埋完毕后，于其上面覆盖一层粘土和一层壤土，使垃圾密封起来，防止雨水下渗和对环境产生污染，同时为植被恢复和景观配置提供基础。在封场处理后，重建以植被为主的人工生态系统。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">五、环境影响评价结论要点<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">本项目拟建于嘉鱼县官桥镇大牛山村一组，项目的建设符合《嘉鱼县城市总体规划（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2008</span>&mdash;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2020</span>）（修编）》中环境卫生规划及环保规划相关要求及《嘉鱼县官桥镇土地利用总体规划》要求，拟选场址具有可行性，本项目实施后，在建设单位充分落实本报告中提出的各项环保措施及相关环境风险应急措施的情况下，运营时所排放的各项污染物可做到达标排放，周围环境质量可控制在可接受范围，从环境保护角度分析，本项目的建设是可行性的。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">六、委托单位的名称和联系方式<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">建设单位：嘉鱼县住房和城乡建设局<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">联系人及电话：彭克华，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0715-6354216<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">七、承担环境影响评价工作的机构和联系方式<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">环境影响评价单位：湖北省环境科学研究院<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">联系人：李刚<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">联系方式：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">027-87654659<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">八、公众提出意见的起止时间<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">公示可在本项目公示之日起<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>日内，以信函、传真、邮件或者其他便利的方式，向建设单位或者评价单位提交意见或建议。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: right; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2012年7月2日</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: right; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: right; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: right; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1673','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-03/67100e8c78d8c828edfd6e6cd2b12975.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n在县经济开发区调研<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>日，县委书记熊征宇、县委副书记李国光、副县长许隆高一行来</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">到县经济开发区和官桥工业园区，调研重点项目建设情况</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">熊征宇一行先后来到洁丽雅纺织嘉鱼产业基地二期、大连成达、中马动力、永幸管业、华亿通橡胶产业园等项目现场，实地了解项目的建设进展，并听取各项目负责人的情况介绍，详细了解项目进展中存在的问题及下一步工作计划。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">在各项目建设现场，运输车辆来回穿梭，各负责领导和责任单位人员对照图纸认真指挥，一派火热景象。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，为推进重点项目建设，我县对当前全县重点项目确定了责任领导、第一责任单位、责任单位，并确定了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度建设内容，督促各项目保证建设质量和加快建设进度。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇要求，项目建设特别是开发区的项目建设要全力推进，各重点项目建设单位要在保证施工质量和安全的前提下，加快建设进度，确保项目能够按照既定时序推进。各相关部门要明确目标责任，强化协调服务，及时帮助解决项目在推进过程中遇到的问题，全力促进项目快建设、早竣工、速达效。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇强调，项目建设环境的整治要真抓真管。对于在项目建设和征地拆迁过程中出现的强揽工程、阻挠施工、乱罚乱收等行为要坚决打击。公安局要安排一名局级领导专门抓环境大整治；要拿出方案、成立专班、设立警务室，对于阻挠项目建设的行为，该打击的必须要打击。他说，居民还建点的建设是征地拆迁顺利进行的重要条件，规划局要加快居民还建点的规划，城投公司要加大资金的投入，鱼岳镇要加大力度，加快居民还建点的建设，为项目建设过程中的征地拆迁创造条件。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委办主任章斌及有关部门负责人陪同调研。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1672','6','耿海军、王芳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/2d7fa668f697713e8325d234fe5bc1f0.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">嘉鱼国际大酒店效果图</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-02/b9eafb0db98926e643191cbb9ed0db32.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">副县长李德炳代表县政府与投资方代表签约</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日，嘉鱼宾馆升级改造项目在县旅游局正式签约。湖北纽兰投资有限公司全资收购嘉鱼宾馆，拆除现有地面建筑后，将按五星级酒店标准在原址重新建设&ldquo;嘉鱼国际大酒店&rdquo;，计划总投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.03</span>亿元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">该项目建筑方案由具甲级建筑设计资质的浙江联建工程设计有限公司规划设计，建筑主体由主楼和裙楼构成，总层高<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">32</span>层，配套地下三层停车场，预计<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>月动工，计划建设工期<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>个月。设计方案中强化了餐饮、娱乐、会务等配套服务功能，着力于提升嘉鱼旅游、商务接待水平。为了提高设计方案的可行性和科学性，县旅游局和投资方邀请了多名国家级星评员对设计方案进行评议，并将行业标准指导贯穿到项目设计、建设、装饰、管理全过程。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">嘉鱼宾馆是我县第一家二星级饭店，于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1996</span>年开业，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2006</span>年改制，近年来由于设施较为陈旧，配套服务缺乏，已不能满足市场要求。升级改造后，或成为我县首家五星级宾馆。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1674','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<div class=\\\\\"Section1\\\\\" style=\\\\\"layout-grid:  15.6pt none\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">嘉政发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]11</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">防震减灾是国家公共安全的重要组成部分，是重要的基础性、公益性事业，关系到广大人民群众生命财产安全和经济社会可持续发展。为深入贯彻落实《国务院关于进一步加强防震减灾工作的意见》（国发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2010]18</span>号）、《湖北省防震减灾条例》、《湖北省人民政府关于进一步加强防震减灾工作的意见》（鄂政发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2011]4</span>号）和咸宁市防震减灾工作会议精神，进一步加强我县防震减灾工作，提高防震减灾能力和水平，结合我县实际，现就有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、指导思想<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">以邓小平理论和&ldquo;三个代表&rdquo;重要思想为指导，深入贯彻落实科学发展观，坚持以人为本，把人民群众的生命安全放在首位，坚持预防为主、防御与救助相结合，依靠科技、依靠法制、依靠群众，全面提高地震监测预报、灾害防御、应急救援能力，形成政府主导、军地协作、专群结合、全社会参与的防震减灾工作格局，最大限度减轻地震灾害损失，为经济社会发展创造良好条件。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、工作目标<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">通过建立健全地震监测预报、震灾预防、紧急救援三大工作体系，不断提高防震减灾社会管理和公共服务水平。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2015</span>年，基本形成科学完善的地震观测系统，能够监测<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.5</span>级以上地震，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>分钟内完成破坏性地震烈度速报；基本完成抗震能力不足的重要建设工程的加固改造，新建、改建、扩建工程全部达到抗震设防要求；建立完善的抗震救援队伍体系；广大人民群众基本掌握防震减灾知识和应急避险技能，社会公众应对地震灾害的能力日益增强。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2020</span>年，我县基本具备综合抗御<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>级左右地震的能力，防震减灾能力大幅提升，争取位居全省前列。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、主要工作<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）扎实做好地震监测预报工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加强地震监测网络建设。完善地震信息网络，新建地震信息节点；增加观测手段，新建强震动观测项目，加强地震预测预报。加强群测群防工作。完善地震宏观测报网、地震灾情速报网、地震知识宣传网和镇防震减灾助理员&ldquo;三网一员&rdquo;网络体系，每个镇明确一名防震减灾助理员和一名地震宏观观测员。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）切实提高震害防御综合能力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、强化建设工程抗震设防要求的监督管理。县人民政府将建设工程的抗震设防要求纳入基本建设管理程序，统一进入政府行政服务中心窗口。地震部门、住建部门要加强抗震设防工作协调，科学确定各类建设工程的抗震设防要求，确保建设工程强制性标准与抗震设防要求的相互衔接；项目审批部门和设计审查部门要把经地震部门确定的工程场地抗震设防要求作为项目审查、设计审核和竣工验收的依据和必备内容。对重大建设工程和可能发生严重次生灾害的建设工程，以及地震研究程度和资料详细程度较差地区的新建、改建、扩建工程，必须严格依法开展地震安全性评价，并按照评价结果进行抗震设防。相关部门要加强对建设工程的勘察、设计、施工、监理、竣工验收等环节的抗震设防质量监督和管理。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、推进农村抗震民居示范工作。加强农村基础设施、公共设施和农民自建房抗震设防的指导管理，结合新农村建设、移民搬迁、村庄整治以及危房改造等，推广适合农村的抗震设计和施工技术，加强工匠培训力度，为农民提供施工图纸，建设农村抗震民居示范工程。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、加强人员密集场所建设工程的抗震设防。抓紧实施中小学校舍安全工程，逐步开展其他学校、医院等人员密集场所建设工程抗震普查、抗震性能鉴定，根据鉴定结果进行加固改造。新建的医院等人员密集场所的建设工程，要按照高于当地房屋建筑的抗震设防要求进行设计和施工。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、提升基础设施的抗震能力。严格落实交通、电力、通信、供水、供气、水利等基础设施的抗震设防标准。加强对危险线段、控制性工程的抗震设防，适当提高抗震设防标准，以增强其紧急情况下的抗灾救灾能力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）着力提升地震应急救援能力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、健全地震应急指挥体系。按照统一指挥、反应迅速、运转高效、保障有力的要求，加强抗震救灾指挥体系建设。完善规章制度，明确职责分工，健全指挥调度、协助联动、信息共享、社会动员等工作机制。修订和完善县、镇二级政府及各部门地震应急预案，进一步增强地震应急预案及相关预案的针对性和可操作性，适时开展预案演练。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、抓好地震灾害救援力量建设。加强我县地震灾害紧急救援队伍建设，建立应急救援装备保障、经费保障和队伍训练机制，适应我县地震救援任务和周边地区地震应急支援的需求。建立和健全军地地震应急救援协调机制，充分发挥解放军、武警部队在抗震救灾中的主力军作用。规范有序地发挥志愿者和民间救援力量的作用。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、推进应急避难场所建设。将应急避难场所建设纳入城市建设规划统筹安排。学校、医院、影剧院、商场、酒店、体育场馆等人员密集场所要设置地震应急疏散通道，配备必要的救生避险设施。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、完善应急物资储备保障体系。加强我县救灾物资储备体系建设，抓好救灾物质设备的质量安全监管，鼓励引导社会力量开展应急物资储备。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">四、保障措施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）加强对防震减灾工作的领导。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">县人民政府将把防震减灾工作列入重要议事日程，及时研究解决影响防震减灾事业发展的突出问题，并纳入政府年度工作目标考核。要将防震减灾工作规划、城市抗震设防专项规划分别纳入地方国民经济和社会发展总体规划和城市建设总体规划。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）建立防震减灾工作体系。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">建立健全工作协调、情况通报、检查督办三大机制，形成齐抓共管、整体联动、合力推进的工作体系。地震部门负责防震减灾工作的组织、协调和指导，发改、住建、规划执法等有关部门配合抓好抗震防设工作。要把防震减灾知识纳入中小学公共安全教育课程，并作为领导干部和公务员培训教育的重要内容，加强防震减灾科普知识的公益性宣传。各相关部门都要依法履行职责，形成工作合力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）抓好地震机构和队伍建设。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">不断巩固充实我县地震人才队伍，完善机构设置，加强人员配备，使组织建设与防震减灾工作任务适应。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）加大经费投入力度。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">县人民政府将把防震减灾工作经费列入本级财政年度预算，并根据工作需要和经济发展，建立动态增长机制，保障防震减灾工作的顺利开展。根据我县实际情况，从<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年开始，我县设立防震减灾专项资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>万元，并随着财政收入的增长和防震减灾工作的需要逐年增加。防震减灾专项资金要按照有关法规和政策规定专款专用。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">O</span>一二年六月十三日<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1675','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]78</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.3pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.95; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2012</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">年是实施交通物流发展&ldquo;十二五&rdquo;规划承上启下重要的一年，也是构建我县综合交通运输体系、加快综合运输枢纽建设、大力推进城乡一体化关键的一年。近年来，物流业中央投资项目和省预算内项目逐年增加，国家重点倾斜的有农产品批发市场、粮食现代物流、物流业重点工程、粮油仓储设施、农产品冷链物流等五个方面的项目。为抢抓项目发展机遇，全面了解我县农村产业基础和资源优势，引导我县农村物流健康有序发展<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>经研究，在全县开展一次农副特产品全面调查。特将有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.3pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.95; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、此次调查工作由县物流发展局牵头，成立以金敬东为组长、尹强为副组长、任勇等为成员的调查专班。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.3pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.95; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、调查内容为农副特产品：种类、产量、主要销售地及运输方式等。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.3pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.95; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、各镇要落实专人，深入农副特生产基地、企业、市场进行专访<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">;</span>要做到部署详细、范围全面、内容真实、数据准确。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.3pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.95; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、县直相关单位要积极配合，协助调查专班做好相关工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.3pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.95; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、调查完毕后，各镇将调查结果汇总，并将调查报告以及调查表以书面形式，于<st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"7\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日</st1:chsdate>前上报县物流发展局。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.3pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.95; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">联系人：任勇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>电<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span>话：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13307247817<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\